<h1> Create, Read, Update, Delete</h1>
<p> <i>a simple demonstration</i> </p>

<div class="container col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1">
<div  class="col-sm-10"><form > <span> type something, the click create&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><input id="thing_name" type="text"></form></div>
<div class="col-sm-2" id="create" >
  <p>Create</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="container col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1">
<div  class="col-sm-5"><form > <span> identify the document by adding the current time value here&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><input id="update_time" type="text"></form></div>
<div  class="col-sm-5"><form > <span> add the new name value here, then click update&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><input id="update_name" type="text"></form></div>
<div class="col-sm-2" id="update" >
  <p>Update</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="container col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1">
<div  class="col-sm-10"><form > <span> delete by searching an Id value&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><input id="delete_name" type="text"></form></div>
<div class="col-sm-2" id="delete" >
  <p>Delete</p>
</div>
</div>
